                                        <p>
                        <persName key="d1e12738" xml:id="d1e134397">M., <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#284077" xml:id="d1e134399" corresp="abbaye Saint-Julien d'Auxerre (635 -)">Sancti Juliani
                                Altissiodorensis</orgName> abbatissa</persName>, omnibus presentes
                        litteras inspecturis salutem. Universitati vestre notum <lb n="2" /> fieri
                        volumus quod dominus <persName key="d1e12744" xml:id="d1e134405">Amauricus,
                            canonicus de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#284077" xml:id="d1e134407" corresp="abbaye Saint-Julien d'Auxerre (635 -)">Sancto
                                Juliano</orgName>, presbiter de <orgName key="stutzmann_himanis#284103" xml:id="d1e134410" corresp="abbaye Saint-Martin d'Autun (599 -)">Sancto Martino</orgName>
                        </persName>, in presentia nostra <lb n="3" /> et conventus nostri
                        constitutus, in ipso capitulo nostro, pro remedio anime sue, in perpetuam
                        elemosinam vineam <lb n="4" /> suam de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324898" xml:id="d1e134417" corresp="Meurgers (Les) (Côte-d'Or, Is-sur-Tille)">
                            <foreign>Murgers</foreign>
                        </placeName> ecclesie et conventui de <placeName key="stutzmann_himanis#324453" xml:id="d1e134422" corresp="Fontenay (Côte-d'Or, Montbard)">
                            <foreign>Fontenai</foreign>
                        </placeName> concessit et donavit. In cujus rei memoriam presen<lb n="5" break="no" />tes litteras sigillo nostro munitas predicte ecclesie et
                        conventui prefato tradere curavimus. Actum ab in<lb n="6" break="no" />carnatione Domini anno .M°. CC°. XI°. <figure rend="trait" />
                    </p>
                
